@startuml ALLSTRM_Sequence_Meeting
!theme plain

actor Client
participant Gateway
participant SFU
participant Core

Client -> Gateway: WS Connect
Client -> Gateway: JOIN_REQUEST
Gateway -> SFU: POST /join
SFU -> Core: Get Room
Core --> SFU: Room Info
SFU --> Gateway: JOIN_ACCEPTED (participants, ICE servers)
Gateway --> Client: JOIN_ACCEPTED
Client -> Gateway: OFFER (SDP)
Gateway -> SFU: POST /offer
SFU --> Gateway: SDP answer
Gateway --> Client: ANSWER
Client -> Gateway: ICE_CANDIDATE
Gateway -> SFU: POST /ice
Client -> SFU: WebRTC Media (Audio/Video)
Gateway --> Client: PARTICIPANT_JOINED (broadcast)
@enduml